					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13094893#post-4525870</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13094893/all-in-all-you-re-just-a-nother-brick-in-the-wall#post-4525870</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2020 18:55:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DrBleep</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2887044</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You know, this wasn't originally supposed to be its own tale, but a part of my 001 itself, but I kept getting feedback from folks who said there was a potential emotional core here that could work as a standalone tale that would still build towards the ultimate goal of establishing things for my 001&#8230; and here we are about 4 months later, through multiple drafting stages, and me pestering a crap ton of folks to look at this. Welcome to the first piece in a larger series of tales setting the stage for what I hope will be a cataclysmic and raucous 001.</p> <p>Huge thanks to everyone who looked over, reviewed, and critted this thing. I'm very proud of how far along its come, and I'm very excited to reintroduce people to two characters who I very much love dearly. Get ready for the roller-coaster.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Show&nbsp;Crit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Hide&nbsp;Critt</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span> Huge thanks to MCB for tolerating my constant pestering, inquiries, and critique requests over multiple iterations. He played a phenomenally large role in helping assess whether my tone/dialogue was consistent and worked. All those small suggestions led to some of the best characterization of these two characters I've been able to put to paper.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span> Kirby gave me some critical advice which led to sussing out and really nailing down the core tone of Sherry's emotional break, and his suggestions I think really hardcore carried the emotional core of the piece into what it is now.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span> Huge thanks to Zyn for reviewing for tone, grammar, and giving some advice on general formatting and trimming out fat.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span> For having a read and reviewing for tone/grammar/spag.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" >Elogee FishTruck</a></span> For reading and giving SpaG and Tone critique.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span> For reading<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span> For Reading<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span> For reading and crit about ending tone/whiplash<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fantem" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1391641&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Fantem" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1391641)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fantem" >Fantem</a></span> For the original idea to turn this into a tale.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ethagon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5844683&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Ethagon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5844683)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ethagon" >Ethagon</a></span> For reading.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span> For reading and critt.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span> For reading<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1552358&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="HammerMaiden" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1552358)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" >HammerMaiden</a></span> For reading<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> For Reading and Crit<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3118444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Pedantique" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3118444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedantique" >Pedantique</a></span> for Reading and Crit, his critt helped me polish down the last bits of the rough edges.<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyvstvi13" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6004508&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583088899" alt="Cyvstvi13" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6004508)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyvstvi13" >Cyvstvi13</a></span> For reading and Crit</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
